0Gora is an original implementation composed from open-source libraries. Its
design was influenced by open-source enterprise-search platforms (e.g. Onyx,
MIT-licensed) and the broader RAG ecosystem; it is not a fork of any of them.

AI inference is executed and cryptographically verified on the 0G network via
the 0G serving broker (@0glabs/0g-serving-broker). "0G", "0GM", and related
marks belong to the 0G Foundation and are used here for descriptive purposes
only; this project is not affiliated with or endorsed by the 0G Foundation.
